Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:04.85,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:05.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:08.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:10.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:11.49,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.07,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that you \Nshould kiss Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Either way, why would I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:19.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's needed for her to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And why would that need a k-kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.54,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:26.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.38,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:28.29,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to \Nget that mad at girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:30.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:42.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.21,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:46.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:29.04,Episode-Title - Copy - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-One: \N The Messenger from the Bottom of the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.54,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.00,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.80,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.47,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's not gonna come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.15,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,She left in a pretty big hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.07,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Hii.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.84,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.02,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I leave you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.03,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be off, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.57,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:04.22,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, don't push Manaka-chan too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.14,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag her around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.58,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You always go running ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.38,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,If she starts not to feel well—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:19.12,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-chan, you can make Hikari \Ndo anything you need him to, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.30,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.05,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka, I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.61,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.57,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,so you can take your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, you're staying home with mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.52,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:33.30,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka... I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.08,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka! Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.31,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to like you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.62,Saya Mart,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.13,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.16,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're back together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:55.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.66,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,The Four from Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.17,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.80,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,The four of you together are one unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.98,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.76,Always Smiling,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Always Smiling\NSaya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.34,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.25,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.25,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Mukaido I said, "Hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There are five in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have one left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan, it's cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each other in forever and that's what you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, it's cold, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,usually people would be more surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Considering how grown up \Nsome people have gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.44,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't Chii-chan just Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.26,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing field work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So he's on top of the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,He's busy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.44,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.95,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, let's \Ngo to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.99,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,My body got all crackly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.05,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.94,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So when your Ena gets \Ndried up, it gets crackly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:34.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's crackly, \Nor hard to breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time it's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.56,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.44,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Hikari and the others \Ntell you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.32,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,They did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.46,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just gone \Nwith Hikari and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.08,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,He invited you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,The right to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.69,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The... right to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.68,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that was \Ndoing all that research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.46,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not happy about Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.43,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,She finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "She finally woke up..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.33,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy that I was \Nactually happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But something was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.28,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It was different from what I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.70,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what \Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.29,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I'm \Nsupposed to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.34,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You look totally surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.23,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.02,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I don't have any Ena!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.78,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.67,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It really is frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that from the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:17.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But if you see it up close, \Nit's really surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.93,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.96,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,For you, the Ofunehiki was \Njust the other day, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.95,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.24,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much salt-flake snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't this much before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.47,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's like playing spot the \Ndifference or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Spot the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:43.95,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:57.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Closing my eyes and then opening them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I keep finding things that \Nare different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Salt-flake snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Salt-flake snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And even more salt-flake snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep pointing \Nout the salt-flake snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:17.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,{Tehe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.80,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun's being nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... I've always been nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's salt-flake \Nsnow over there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, it's dangerous if you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.49,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What were we even trying so hard for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.00,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Manaka woke up even without
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.18,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,the help of Uroko-sama's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It all worked out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:09:00.21,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it was sort of anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Considering Manaka's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's so full of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chii-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And she just woke up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.68,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,How were you, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.36,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,When you first woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.45,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The town looked familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.44,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,but everything was just slightly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.48,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I was going to \Ndo if everything looked the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.96,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.93,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:39.01,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see any more \Nthings that've changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.85,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think about all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.35,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:48.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she can laugh so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.77,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because \Nyou're here, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.56,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And we are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought she'd want \Nto go see him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She says she doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.25,Wake up Manaka,signs,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right before the Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:21.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No. What happened after the Ofunehiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.47,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You were pulled down to the \Nbottom of the sea... after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I think... I heard someone's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:29.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whose voice was it? \NWas it Uroko-sama's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Uroko-sama's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.27,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It could have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I think they said they'd \Ngive me something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.72,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,or they asked me to \Ngive them something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Give them what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Manaka, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The school's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:12.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,...covered in salt-flake snow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have Ena anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She can't go back to the sea... so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.89,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So why is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.65,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's Manaka for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This part is my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Then I'll do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! You can't have that part anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:53.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This, this, this, and this are all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't have all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.16,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.74,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to school on Sunday \Ndoesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking. What \Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.14,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,S-Studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:16.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd study for some tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.50,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know? Finals are next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about \Ntests all the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.39,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, studying is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.88,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.33,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What were you guys studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,In math, we're learning simultaneous equations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,and in English, we're learning \Nconjunctions and verbal nouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I suck at both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about a downer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Other than arithmetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,you don't really use math anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.67,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd be the idiot's excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.72,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I think studying is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.04,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It is important, isn't it, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It probably would be \Nbetter to study properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.39,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late to regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have to start heading to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.37,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.25,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu's grandfather \Nis in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:15.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty old now, \Nand a lot's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:24.95,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eat these. Sayama-kun gave them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.12,salt_cream_puffs,,0000,0000,0000,,Salt Cream Puffs\N{\fs14}Full of Minerals and made with salt from Oshiooshi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:39.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's just enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.08,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki-san's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.03,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.82,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I do! You want one, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.24,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.06,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well, I had a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I finished up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should have gone to see Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:25.27,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if she saw too much, \Nshe'd probably get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.34,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How was Mukaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She was so full of energy it surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.43,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll come visit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.63,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Want a tangerine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.44,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.07,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There's coffee jelly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps remembered my favorite foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.92,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I might like it more than cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why cream puffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Around the end of the month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.34,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm going back \Nto the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:28.86,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The university's telling the professor \Nto hurry and put together our findings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:46.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I just said the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.39,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When you eat something sweet \Nfirst, it becomes sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.14,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send tangerines to your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.63,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them with all the \Npeople in your lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.00,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:13.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If I find something out, I'll \Ncontact you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What, Tsumugu? Are you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.80,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.03,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, everyone's back now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll have to watch over Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka really hasn't....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't need to worry \Nabout trivial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.20,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do your research at the university!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:55.66,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You and Professor Mihashi are \Nthe only ones able to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There's still so much we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:03.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Manaka woke up and \NHikari and Kaname seem fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,there's so much we \Ndon't even understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:09.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Like what's going to happen in \Nthe sea or on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,the world's future, the \Nweather, and the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could just ask Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because he seems to know \Neverything about the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.06,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling he'd just \Nsay something random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But he is the scale of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tentatively.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.85,0:17:31.11,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So it's tentative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:34.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he'd say \Nanything even if I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's always so contrary,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.07,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention he's perverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.69,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can bribe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Bribe"? You mean money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.38,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,No... like porn mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That might work really well, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.02,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.95,Main,mihashi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.40,Main,mihashi,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.15,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.90,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't push you \Nguys if you can't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.67,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dada, where's Dada?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.61,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dada's going to be late at work tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.52,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't put the \Nfish in all the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The flavor comes out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What'd Tsumugu have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.05,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:28.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.36,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.38,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.22,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, no touching the \Ncrab. It'll be an owie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Something with Tsumugu's grandfather.\NThey apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.26,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are actually studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "actually"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're making it sound like I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're not studying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.58,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be time for entrance \Nexams in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, I think I'll go hibernate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.87,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.36,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu-chan, help Hikari with \Nhis studying, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:56.64,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the smartest in class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.72,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's not sometimes, it's all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.78,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.95,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's applying for \NHama High School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.30,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shishio doesn't \Nhave a high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine with how things are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.09,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you blow on \Nit before eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still hot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.81,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? It doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.09,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.82,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.97,Flashback,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the Sea God is angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.38,Main,ikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.80,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:14.11,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun? Hii-kun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you said you'd tell \Nme after the Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.19,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.07,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,After it's done, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:30.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:31.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.02,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.66,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.42,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're here early, Tsumugu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mukaido here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.17,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.91,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:24.76,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.96,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:44.86,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I was cursed by Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.43,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Cursed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.50,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He a person that curses people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's not actually a person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko's somewhere close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.19,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed a lady and you're \Njust going to leave her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:34.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:35.98,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.48,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll try asking her out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Two: \NSomething Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Asking out, huh...
